{"tid":429252,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"當你心很累時 大家會做啲乜？","createTime":"2017-10-08T17:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T04:58:22.000Z","uid":148482,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb0e7e8438158b6ddd38e48e5cdb8bb04174caf","tid":429252,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"如題 想知大家有冇好方法解累<br />\n同埋希望大家會先講下大概係因咩事而心很累<br />\n<br />\n我先啦<br />\n讀緊音樂 覺得喺學校比唔上其他同學 好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己又樣衰又柒又肥 外貌0分<br />\n喺學校都唔敢喺同學面前練野 一定會呢喺琴房自己練<br />\n<br />\n喺感情方面<br />\n拍過兩次拖 兩次都一齊左兩年<br />\n但兩次都係帽事收場<br />\n當兩個ex都係選擇比帽時 我就覺得問題即係喺我到啦<br />\n如果我夠好 佢地根本唔會比帽我<br />\n宜家有中意嘅女仔都唔敢去追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心真係很累<br />\n有時番到屋企時 真係會呢喺房到自己流馬尿 <br />\n好想放棄所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者會去海旁單機狂飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  借酒消愁<br />\n但講真 啲頹氣同心累感都冇散<br />\n所以想知大家有咩高見可以分享下<br />\n拯救下小弟"},{"pid":"a2ba5d7efdf762e892d5c3ecd9ae1fe5870db15f","tid":429252,"uid":68961,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:14:10.000Z","msg":"約fd出黎啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前我又係係第二到讀書，心累到爆，唔知人生存黎做乜個隻<br />\n之後好彩有d時間以家飛返香港一陣見fd，即刻差足電咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過後日又要走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d6c26321115baa506f95eec843cd6762040cdc","tid":429252,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>約fd出黎啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前我又係係第二到讀書，心累到爆，唔知人生存黎做乜個隻<br />\n之後好彩有d時間以家飛返香港一陣見fd，即刻差足電咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過後日又要走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲中同都各有各忙 好難約得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家嘅同學個個都chur住練習 真係好獨毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個心愈講愈累呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc753b949b0edd345d84acb49e970d48848684f","tid":429252,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21fbbfaa7327f48b6c4aed5ad517977933babb9a","tid":429252,"uid":104687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:28:05.000Z","msg":"祈禱"},{"pid":"a3724a93f05987c8678e619039fe17156d7ca2db","tid":429252,"uid":64401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"因為我玩喇叭，所以我會一邊聽古典一邊睇上綱器材，好relaxing 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e4d10a2328afe00365062d8b2b68284ac5b38e","tid":429252,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同friend打機</blockquote><br />\n宜家連打機嘅時間都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電腦同PS4都封哂塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打打完機真係會解心累？"},{"pid":"20a6ed22ffcc01a734118b463f9d2b412487b7ea","tid":429252,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祈禱</blockquote><br />\n希望絲打可以比個祝福我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644969ea4104d302acc191b74d62a68c3bb00043","tid":429252,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為我玩喇叭，所以我會一邊聽古典一邊睇上綱器材，好relaxing 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我平時都成日聽Classical music<br />\n但係個壓力仍然好大 <br />\n有時仲因為啲test要背歌 所以身心更加疲累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71e914b3760be906390ef5e156197692559a6a9","tid":429252,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"巴打邊頭讀？"},{"pid":"ac16e0a6b1c6dac5ae8811b38f14e55b1d3650a7","tid":429252,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打邊頭讀？</blockquote><br />\n港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8909aeba62c8bcfa7bee8122e06b227dcbcef2e9","tid":429252,"uid":152309,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:03:46.000Z","msg":"面對現實繼續向前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94096022040ddd5f7172cb660fb6f15921328fe","tid":429252,"uid":105665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"冇朋友可以點算<br />\n好認真問<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"8f9486b9e340016af6b4764e7abf159303059f3f","tid":429252,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9b2e510904e968e0f9d3d34f12eb0f719f2fd66","tid":429252,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:04:37.000Z","msg":"讀邊方面音樂"},{"pid":"e85ce714faf19bf192c8d8e97400150228ef544b","tid":429252,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀邊方面音樂</blockquote><br />\nClassical music<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a18ea484fd3c6198185f